c: 9
v: 100
t: "Allah asepeli na bandimi ya liboso baye batikaki (Makkah) na baye bayambaki bango, (na Madinah) lolenge moko na basusu baye bayaki sima na bango na bolamu, bango mpe basepeli naye. Mpe abongiseli bango Iola eye ezali koleka o nsé na yango mingala, bakozalaka libela na libela kati na yango, wana nde elonga enene"